28/03/2003
PODGORICA, Serbia-Montenegro -- Montenegrin Prime Minister Milo Djukanovic has sought the assistance of the OSCE in implementing media laws, in light of the 11 May presidential elections. 
His office says Djukanovic discussed the issue at length Thursday (27 March) during a meeting with OSCE Mission Chief Maurizio Massari. 
(B92, BBC - 27/03/03)
